Try and mix up the hues of pink that you’re wearing as this will add a point of difference to your look, but remember to pair it with something that’s fairly subdued to balance out your look. <img class="aligncenter wp-image-1103103 lazyload" src="https://guardian.ng/wp-content/uploads/2020/02/Skibii-in-a-pink-jacket-Photo-MyGbedu-498x598.jpg" alt="" width="1280" height="1537" srcset="https://guardian.ng/wp-content/uploads/2020/02/Skibii-in-a-pink-jacket-Photo-MyGbedu-498x598.jpg 498w,https://guardian.ng/wp-content/uploads/2020/02/Skibii-in-a-pink-jacket-Photo-MyGbedu-959x1152.jpg 959w,https://guardian.ng/wp-content/uploads/2020/02/Skibii-in-a-pink-jacket-Photo-MyGbedu-464x557.jpg 464w,https://guardian.ng/wp-content/uploads/2020/02/Skibii-in-a-pink-jacket-Photo-MyGbedu-928x1114.jpg 928w,https://guardian.ng/wp-content/uploads/2020/02/Skibii-in-a-pink-jacket-Photo-MyGbedu-200x240.jpg 200w,https://guardian.ng/wp-content/uploads/2020/02/Skibii-in-a-pink-jacket-Photo-MyGbedu-400x480.jpg 400w,https://guardian.ng/wp-content/uploads/2020/02/Skibii-in-a-pink-jacket-Photo-MyGbedu-500x600.jpg 500w,https://guardian.ng/wp-content/uploads/2020/02/Skibii-in-a-pink-jacket-Photo-MyGbedu.jpg 1080w" sizes="(max-width: 1280px) 100vw, 1280px" /> Pink As An Accessory
If you’re more of a shrinking violet, experiment with smaller, subtle pieces that are worn away from the skin such as a pocket square or a flash of a pink sock.  